channel.title: Just a few questions. (Not about making a server)
channel.description: Er...hey! Okay, to the point. I've always wondered HOW THE HECK do we get runescape's cache? I heard from someone that JaGex has it on our computers, but what? Can someone please explain how we get runescape 2's cache? Thanks. Now I have another question, about Aryan, what exactly is it? Thanks!
